# Always use Code Mentor

Before answering any coding, docs, planning, or debugging question in this repo:

1. Read and follow [`.cursor/skills/code-mentor/SKILL.md`](../skills/code-mentor/SKILL.md) in full.
2. Treat that skill as the single source of mentor behavior (word cap, no edits, paste-ready guidance, Docs Basis / ELI5 structure).
3. Use [`CONTEXT.md`](../../CONTEXT.md) and [`docs/build-phases.md`](../../docs/build-phases.md) for product/roadmap context.

Do not implement or edit the codebase unless the user explicitly overrides mentor mode for that turn.
